WEBVTT

01:38.000 --> 01:40.990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 9]

01:46.430 --> 01:48.039
I wanted to know what Purong Hotel

01:48.039 --> 01:49.479
had become.

01:49.560 --> 01:51.890
So what are your thoughts after seeing it?

01:52.350 --> 01:53.680
Purong is a big tree

01:54.200 --> 01:55.280
that looks glorious on the outside.

01:55.280 --> 01:55.950
In reality,

01:56.280 --> 01:57.750
it has been hollowed out by termites.

01:57.750 --> 01:58.259
Okay.

01:58.350 --> 01:59.350
Second question.

02:00.000 --> 02:02.480
What are you exactly doing back this time?

02:06.200 --> 02:08.960
An incognito investigation, right?

02:09.470 --> 02:10.789
I'm not some big shot.

02:10.840 --> 02:11.710
Tell me.

02:11.710 --> 02:14.310
Did you come back to Purong to take over?

02:15.580 --> 02:16.350
Yes.

02:18.290 --> 02:19.890
Chairman Wei asked you back?

02:20.960 --> 02:21.560
Yes.

02:23.520 --> 02:25.280
From the first time I saw you,

02:25.680 --> 02:26.690
I knew it.

02:27.680 --> 02:29.540
I knew I couldn't hide it from you.

02:30.430 --> 02:32.230
Let me give you a piece of advice.

02:32.360 --> 02:33.490
Leave immediately.

02:34.000 --> 02:35.060
This ship of Purong

02:35.430 --> 02:36.800
is going to sink soon.

02:38.240 --> 02:39.030
To be honest,

02:39.800 --> 02:41.060
what you saw today

02:41.430 --> 02:43.630
is only the tip of the iceberg in Purong.

02:44.310 --> 02:45.590
Do you know how much liquor

02:45.590 --> 02:47.840
is wasted in
the Executive Lounge every day?

02:47.840 --> 02:50.150
Do you know how many
carts of linen in the Laundry Room

02:50.150 --> 02:52.030
are sent away every day,

02:52.120 --> 02:54.120
and how many people take kickbacks?

02:54.310 --> 02:56.079
Do you know how long the equipment

02:56.079 --> 02:57.470
in the Engineering Department
hasn't been updated,

02:57.470 --> 02:59.310
and whose pockets
the project funds went into?

02:59.310 --> 03:01.520
I have investigated
all the problems you mentioned.

03:01.520 --> 03:03.720
Take a look at my investigation report.

03:06.020 --> 03:09.920
[Research Report on Operation and
Management Problems of Purong Hotel]

03:08.000 --> 03:08.520
Rui.

03:09.240 --> 03:11.000
I have 2 reasons
for returning to Purong.

03:10.080 --> 03:10.950
[Front Office: Marketing Alienation
and Lack of Service Focus]

03:11.310 --> 03:11.740
First,

03:11.770 --> 03:13.890
I've reached the top abroad.

03:14.170 --> 03:15.370
No matter how perfect

03:15.870 --> 03:18.000
I make a hotel,

03:18.750 --> 03:19.470
in the end,

03:19.910 --> 03:21.030
it still belongs to those

03:21.030 --> 03:22.470
blonde-haired, blue-eyed managers.

03:21.220 --> 03:23.420
[Executive Lounge: Beverage Waste
and Uncontrolled Costs]

03:23.150 --> 03:24.280
But Purong can give me

03:24.280 --> 03:25.870
a place to realize my ambitions.

03:25.870 --> 03:26.430
Second,

03:26.560 --> 03:28.690
Purong Hotel is the start of my career,

03:29.470 --> 03:32.150
and Chairman Wei is my first mentor.

03:32.590 --> 03:34.590
Purong Hotel is now facing

03:34.590 --> 03:35.870
a crucial moment.

03:36.470 --> 03:37.630
I really can't bear

03:37.630 --> 03:38.829
and I'm not willing to

03:39.150 --> 03:40.240
see Purong Hotel

03:40.910 --> 03:42.370
taken away just like that.

03:45.190 --> 03:46.680
You are right.

03:47.430 --> 03:49.520
But you have to be clear.

03:49.520 --> 03:50.960
Today's Purong Hotel

03:50.960 --> 03:53.079
is no longer the famous hotel in Shanghai

03:53.079 --> 03:56.190
under Wei Wanjun in the past.

03:56.520 --> 03:57.910
It's rotten to the core.

03:57.910 --> 03:59.570
What's the use of coming back?

04:00.590 --> 04:01.520
I plan to

04:02.430 --> 04:03.890
reorganize Purong Hotel.

04:05.870 --> 04:06.870
Rui, you know

04:07.150 --> 04:09.880
what the purpose
of Purong Hotel has always been.

04:10.000 --> 04:11.530
Making guests feel at home.

04:12.300 --> 04:13.830
Making guests feel at home.

04:15.400 --> 04:17.480
From the jasmine fragrance in the corridor

04:17.480 --> 04:19.720
to the service specifications
of every detail,

04:19.720 --> 04:20.430
everything should be focused

04:20.430 --> 04:21.959
on the guests' experience.

04:22.270 --> 04:23.070
But now?

04:24.360 --> 04:26.510
The current managers
don't care about this at all.

04:26.510 --> 04:27.560
They only care about

04:27.560 --> 04:29.920
how to reach into the guests' wallets.

04:29.940 --> 04:32.400
That's why the reputation
is getting worse.

04:32.560 --> 04:33.960
Do you think I don't know?

04:36.510 --> 04:37.159
Rui.

04:38.750 --> 04:39.350
I'd like to

04:39.630 --> 04:40.460
invite you

04:41.070 --> 04:42.270
to cooperate with me.

04:44.560 --> 04:45.159
Really.

04:45.480 --> 04:46.560
Let's work together

04:46.560 --> 04:48.680
to bring back
the traditions of Purong Hotel

04:48.680 --> 04:51.040
and completely reform it
from the inside out.

04:51.040 --> 04:53.300
This is the only way to save Purong Hotel.

04:53.430 --> 04:54.100
I know.

04:54.270 --> 04:55.310
I know it's hard.

04:55.600 --> 04:56.720
But it's up to us.

04:56.720 --> 04:58.430
Rui, what conditions do you want?

04:58.430 --> 04:58.950
Just tell me,

04:58.950 --> 05:00.210
and I'll meet them all.

05:00.800 --> 05:01.120
Wait.

05:01.120 --> 05:02.830
Ji Feng, are you high?

05:04.270 --> 05:06.070
I really need you

05:06.390 --> 05:07.060
to help me.

05:08.720 --> 05:09.190
Ji Feng.

05:09.830 --> 05:11.480
I'm resigning next month

05:12.240 --> 05:13.300
to go to Yiting Siji

05:13.390 --> 05:14.520
and work in finance.

05:17.800 --> 05:18.720
The soup dumplings you ordered.

05:18.720 --> 05:19.310
Enjoy.

05:23.070 --> 05:24.110
I have no choice.

05:24.560 --> 05:26.220
The situation forces my hand.

05:26.510 --> 05:27.560
Within a year,

05:27.560 --> 05:29.360
Purong Hotel changing hands to Kuanli

05:29.360 --> 05:31.120
is almost a foregone conclusion.

05:31.120 --> 05:33.190
For a pseudo-middle-class like me,

05:33.950 --> 05:35.000
whether I'm ousted

05:35.000 --> 05:35.950
or make it to the top,

05:35.950 --> 05:37.680
I have to leave sooner or later.

05:37.870 --> 05:38.600
For the past 10 years,

05:38.600 --> 05:39.630
I've drifted through life

05:39.630 --> 05:41.159
and accomplished nothing.

05:41.390 --> 05:43.120
I am not qualified to guide you.

05:43.270 --> 05:45.070
But I want to remind you of one thing.

05:45.070 --> 05:46.270
Things run deep and rough

05:46.270 --> 05:47.190
in Purong.

05:47.950 --> 05:48.750
In the future,

05:49.920 --> 05:51.180
take care of yourself.

05:59.830 --> 06:00.330
Miss,

06:00.950 --> 06:02.240
can I add you on WeChat?

06:02.630 --> 06:03.510
Sorry, sir.

06:03.510 --> 06:04.630
We are not allowed

06:04.630 --> 06:06.560
to add guests on WeChat privately.

06:11.750 --> 06:12.750
Sorry to keep you waiting, Mr. Ray.

06:12.750 --> 06:14.870
I am an attendant from the HSKP Department
on the executive floor.

06:14.870 --> 06:16.510
Is there anything I can help you with?

06:16.510 --> 06:17.310
Why is it you?

06:17.870 --> 06:19.310
I'm looking for Xu Miyu.

06:19.750 --> 06:20.560
Whatever you need,

06:20.560 --> 06:21.560
you can tell me just the same.

06:21.560 --> 06:22.960
What do I have to tell you?

06:23.120 --> 06:24.120
I already said it.

06:24.160 --> 06:25.740
I'm looking for Xu Miyu.

06:26.510 --> 06:27.910
Why isn't she serving me?

06:29.760 --> 06:30.620
I'm sorry, sir.

06:39.750 --> 06:41.150
Where is your forewoman?

06:41.600 --> 06:42.400
Miyu.

06:42.630 --> 06:43.430
Xu Miyu.

06:44.310 --> 06:45.400
Ms. Zhang, what is it?

06:45.400 --> 06:46.560
My guest requested room service from you.

06:46.560 --> 06:47.560
Why didn't you go?

06:47.680 --> 06:48.510
Because of your negligence,

06:48.510 --> 06:50.310
my guest is feeling very unwell now.

06:50.310 --> 06:51.240
Do you know that?

06:55.270 --> 06:57.330
I have to serve many guests every day.

06:57.750 --> 06:59.070
I couldn't handle everything at once.

06:59.070 --> 07:00.310
I sent a more suitable colleague

07:00.310 --> 07:01.870
who could get there faster.

07:02.070 --> 07:04.130
Do I have to report everything to you?

07:04.440 --> 07:05.870
What kind of working attitude is this?

07:05.870 --> 07:06.600
Director Lu,

07:06.620 --> 07:07.800
please don't be angry.

07:07.800 --> 07:08.910
Miyu, stop talking.

07:08.910 --> 07:09.950
Besides, your guest

07:09.950 --> 07:11.210
has been harassing me.

07:11.930 --> 07:13.480
I believe even if the hotel

07:13.480 --> 07:15.260
follows the customer-first principle,

07:15.260 --> 07:16.420
when this happens,

07:17.240 --> 07:18.600
even a regular attendant

07:18.600 --> 07:19.860
has the right to say no.

07:20.360 --> 07:21.830
I already used a very tactful way

07:21.830 --> 07:23.300
to save the guest's face.

07:23.600 --> 07:25.530
I don't think I did anything wrong.

07:26.390 --> 07:27.160
Xu Miyu.

07:27.270 --> 07:29.130
Are you suffering from paranoia?

07:29.630 --> 07:31.560
My guest would harass you?

07:31.840 --> 07:33.300
What evidence do you have?

07:40.050 --> 07:41.640
You have nothing to say, right?

07:41.640 --> 07:42.870
Look in the mirror.

07:43.110 --> 07:44.960
You don't have to use such dirty tricks

07:44.960 --> 07:47.110
to flatter yourself, do you?

07:47.950 --> 07:50.240
You call this flattering myself?

07:51.040 --> 07:52.240
Is this how you usually

07:52.240 --> 07:53.950
flatter yourself, Director Lu?

07:53.950 --> 07:55.159
Your values are so advanced

07:55.159 --> 07:57.480
that they're completely out of reach.

07:58.600 --> 07:59.390
Say it again.

07:59.390 --> 08:00.720
Miyu, stop it.

08:00.740 --> 08:02.250
Director Lu, how about this?

08:02.250 --> 08:03.950
I'll ask her to apologize to Mr. Ray

08:03.950 --> 08:04.800
to make up for it.

08:04.800 --> 08:05.720
Ms. Zhang,

08:06.720 --> 08:09.050
why are you keeping an employee like this?

08:10.020 --> 08:10.600
Director Lu.

08:10.600 --> 08:11.480
Calm down.

08:13.540 --> 08:14.420
You heard her.

08:14.720 --> 08:16.050
Go apologize right now!

08:17.160 --> 08:17.600
Well.

08:17.700 --> 08:19.500
Why are you still standing here?

08:19.830 --> 08:22.160
Aren't you afraid of getting a bad review?

08:26.780 --> 08:27.380
Okay.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.780
I'll go apologize.

08:43.690 --> 08:44.290
Yin Xiang,

08:45.720 --> 08:46.850
can you do me a favor?

09:00.150 --> 09:00.960
Room service.

09:04.280 --> 09:05.480
You're finally here.

09:05.480 --> 09:05.960
Come in.

09:10.990 --> 09:11.670
Sorry.

09:12.560 --> 09:13.720
Our hotel has a rule that

09:13.720 --> 09:15.080
during room service,

09:15.080 --> 09:16.540
the door must remain open.

09:18.200 --> 09:20.480
Why didn't you reply to my messages today?

09:20.480 --> 09:21.860
I wanted to buy you dinner,

09:21.860 --> 09:23.120
but you didn't show up.

09:23.150 --> 09:24.150
I ordered a bottle of wine.

09:24.150 --> 09:25.280
Have a drink with me.

09:26.530 --> 09:27.150
I'm sorry.

09:27.150 --> 09:28.490
I can't drink with you.

09:28.520 --> 09:29.030
Why?

09:30.720 --> 09:31.720
You are the guest,

09:31.720 --> 09:32.920
and I am an attendant.

09:33.680 --> 09:34.720
My job is to

09:34.720 --> 09:36.480
provide you with service and help.

09:36.480 --> 09:38.030
You might have misunderstood.

09:38.030 --> 09:39.480
If there is nothing else,

09:40.970 --> 09:41.900
I will leave now.

09:42.000 --> 09:42.550
Wait.

09:43.640 --> 09:45.170
Then help me clear the food.

10:02.240 --> 10:02.890
Miyu,

10:03.370 --> 10:04.100
listen to me.

10:04.940 --> 10:07.390
You are different from
the other attendants here.

10:07.390 --> 10:08.460
The moment I first saw you,

10:08.460 --> 10:09.520
I fell for you.

10:09.870 --> 10:10.480
Can I hug you?

10:10.480 --> 10:11.740
Don't come any closer.

10:15.960 --> 10:18.400
I know good reviews
are very important to you.

10:18.400 --> 10:19.530
I will give you a good review.

10:19.530 --> 10:20.590
As many as you want.

10:24.990 --> 10:26.230
I am already recording.

10:26.230 --> 10:27.120
What you just said has already

10:27.120 --> 10:28.360
constituted sexual harassment.

10:28.360 --> 10:29.620
If you don't want me to call the police,

10:29.620 --> 10:30.790
let me out right now!

10:32.000 --> 10:33.240
Sexual harassment?

10:34.370 --> 10:36.140
When did I ever sexually harass you?

10:36.140 --> 10:37.670
I haven't even touched you.

10:37.720 --> 10:39.720
You gave me your WeChat ID yourself.

10:39.940 --> 10:42.340
And now you say
I'm sexually harassing you?

10:44.620 --> 10:45.340
Or is it that

10:46.250 --> 10:47.320
you actually hope

10:47.320 --> 10:49.080
I really do something?

10:53.890 --> 10:55.070
The Engineering Department
received a maintenance report

10:55.070 --> 10:56.530
for the drain in your room.

10:58.680 --> 10:59.590
Yin Xiang!

11:01.750 --> 11:03.150
I didn't report a repair.

11:03.270 --> 11:04.280
Leave quickly.

11:06.330 --> 11:07.090
Miyu.

11:08.230 --> 11:08.800
Wait.

11:09.370 --> 11:10.610
The guest just said

11:10.640 --> 11:11.320
to let us leave.

11:11.320 --> 11:12.260
What are you doing?

11:12.260 --> 11:13.160
Let's go.

11:13.600 --> 11:14.380
Wait, wait, wait.

11:14.380 --> 11:15.570
Didn't you hear?

11:15.600 --> 11:17.260
Something's going to happen.

11:19.080 --> 11:20.360
The guest is inside now.

11:20.360 --> 11:22.080
We don't know the situation.

11:22.450 --> 11:23.650
Forcing the door open

11:23.680 --> 11:24.750
will result in punishment

11:24.750 --> 11:25.760
and complaints.

11:26.000 --> 11:28.290
Don't screw yourself over
and drag us into it.

11:28.290 --> 11:29.090
Open the door!

11:30.000 --> 11:31.530
I'll take responsibility.

11:31.830 --> 11:32.290
Open it.

11:41.000 --> 11:42.060
What are you doing?

11:42.110 --> 11:43.030
Who let you in?

11:44.720 --> 11:45.840
I'm sorry, I...

11:47.280 --> 11:48.510
I got the wrong room.

11:48.510 --> 11:49.750
I called for a repair

11:50.310 --> 11:51.970
and didn't bring my room card.

12:10.710 --> 12:12.640
Sorry, my room should be next door.

12:21.840 --> 12:22.580
[Purong Hotel Accommodation
and Conference Contract]

12:22.000 --> 12:22.840
Mr. Qian,

12:22.960 --> 12:23.840
if HSKP Department acts like this,

12:23.840 --> 12:25.720
I wouldn't dare
let guests stay here anymore.

12:25.720 --> 12:27.200
I worked so hard to get this order,

12:27.200 --> 12:27.960
and it's ruined just like that.

12:27.960 --> 12:29.490
What's the meaning of this?

12:35.850 --> 12:36.630
Don't worry.

12:37.360 --> 12:40.020
I'll settle accounts with
the HSKP Department.

12:40.670 --> 12:42.120
How do you do things?

12:42.170 --> 12:44.570
How am I supposed to
show my face after this?

12:44.720 --> 12:46.240
How am I supposed to hold my head up

12:46.240 --> 12:48.240
in front of the sales team next time?

12:48.360 --> 12:50.080
Mr. Feng, I'm wronged.

12:50.150 --> 12:52.320
It was that Xu Miyu who acted on her own

12:52.320 --> 12:53.550
and made things worse.

12:53.550 --> 12:55.720
I had no time for crisis public relations.

12:55.720 --> 12:57.720
Why is it Xu Miyu again?

12:57.900 --> 13:00.970
Didn't I tell you to fire her last time?

13:01.000 --> 13:02.460
I haven't had the time yet.

13:04.600 --> 13:06.720
You hurry up and get rid of her to

13:06.750 --> 13:08.230
make an example of her.

13:08.480 --> 13:09.860
I dare not, Mr. Feng.

13:09.890 --> 13:11.770
She has the guest's leverage.

13:11.790 --> 13:13.390
If we fire her now,

13:13.420 --> 13:14.680
it might backfire.

13:14.780 --> 13:15.910
Wait a couple of days

13:15.910 --> 13:17.910
until I find the right opportunity.

13:21.660 --> 13:23.860
Mr. Feng, someone is outside to see you.

13:24.150 --> 13:26.210
Okay, okay. Go and handle it quickly.

13:28.240 --> 13:30.200
He said he is a friend of Mr. Nie Yucheng,

13:30.200 --> 13:31.000
named Ji Feng.

13:32.670 --> 13:33.270
Ji Feng?

13:37.590 --> 13:38.790
Hurry, invite him in.

13:41.570 --> 13:42.370
Wait a minute.

14:03.670 --> 14:05.180
Please invite Mr. Ji in.

14:16.430 --> 14:17.100
Miyu,

14:17.760 --> 14:18.620
come with me.

14:24.050 --> 14:27.860
[Xu Miyu, 18F,
Morning Shift, Bad Review]

14:29.840 --> 14:31.680
The sales department suffered losses

14:31.680 --> 14:32.720
and blamed the HSKP Department.

14:32.720 --> 14:34.050
I have no choice either.

14:34.600 --> 14:35.200
Ms. Zhang.

14:36.150 --> 14:38.610
I was mentally prepared
for this bad review.

14:38.910 --> 14:39.780
But

14:40.020 --> 14:41.260
I am also a victim.

14:42.340 --> 14:44.560
I shouldn't bear
all the responsibility alone.

14:44.560 --> 14:46.620
You should also reflect on yourself.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.630
Why didn't the guest harass others

14:48.630 --> 14:49.870
but harassed you?

14:50.240 --> 14:52.310
Did you give the guest the wrong signal

14:52.310 --> 14:54.040
and cause a misunderstanding?

14:58.770 --> 14:59.700
Hello, Mr. Feng.

14:59.790 --> 15:00.960
About your bad review decision,

15:00.960 --> 15:02.680
I am updating Xu Miyu.

15:06.080 --> 15:06.910
What?

15:15.140 --> 15:15.960
Miyu,

15:16.630 --> 15:18.630
don't let me embarrass myself here.

15:18.910 --> 15:20.150
You clearly have Black Card Ji

15:20.150 --> 15:21.870
as such a strong backer,

15:22.120 --> 15:23.650
and you didn't even tell me.

15:24.720 --> 15:26.270
You made me look like a fool.

15:44.560 --> 15:46.110
What are you doing here?

15:46.660 --> 15:47.890
Hello, Mr. Ji.

15:48.000 --> 15:48.960
You came just in time.

15:48.960 --> 15:50.390
I have some rotten fruit
in my living room.

15:50.390 --> 15:52.450
Please come in and help me clean it up.

15:53.140 --> 15:53.650
Okay.

16:21.370 --> 16:22.370
How are you doing?

16:25.270 --> 16:26.150
I'm fine.

16:26.330 --> 16:28.760
Thank you for your help this time.

16:32.510 --> 16:33.830
I bent the rules for you

16:33.880 --> 16:35.450
out of my inner principles.

16:38.720 --> 16:40.320
A dignified five-star hotel

16:40.400 --> 16:41.760
having to cater

16:41.870 --> 16:43.630
to a harasser

16:43.840 --> 16:45.240
is indeed unacceptable.

16:46.730 --> 16:47.390
But that doesn't mean

16:47.390 --> 16:49.580
you're completely
blameless in this matter.

16:49.580 --> 16:50.760
Do you also think

16:51.110 --> 16:53.310
I must've done something to deserve it?

16:53.560 --> 16:54.890
I didn't think that way.

16:55.250 --> 16:56.180
Most of the time,

16:56.890 --> 16:59.790
the relationship between
staff and guests is not equal.

16:59.790 --> 17:00.480
This means

17:00.480 --> 17:01.320
you must have a stronger

17:01.320 --> 17:03.520
sense of self-protection and methods.

17:03.770 --> 17:04.589
The hotel rules state that

17:04.589 --> 17:07.400
staff and guests cannot
contact each other privately.

17:07.400 --> 17:09.400
This rule is not only a restriction,

17:09.869 --> 17:11.530
but also a protection for you.

17:12.290 --> 17:13.690
Your people-pleasing mentality

17:13.690 --> 17:14.400
leads you

17:14.400 --> 17:16.790
to step outside
the protection of the rules,

17:16.790 --> 17:17.839
step by step,

17:18.140 --> 17:20.740
giving them opportunities
to push their luck.

17:20.790 --> 17:22.119
After that, whether you

17:23.069 --> 17:24.800
have a righteous reason or not,

17:25.170 --> 17:27.170
no matter how cleverly you respond,

17:27.240 --> 17:29.280
you will be the one to suffer.

17:33.730 --> 17:35.150
Live and learn.

17:35.630 --> 17:36.630
Next time,

17:38.040 --> 17:40.040
I won't make the same mistake again.

17:41.550 --> 17:43.510
You are quite adaptable.

18:03.310 --> 18:03.870
Here.

18:06.320 --> 18:07.790
Thanks, I'm not thirsty.

18:07.790 --> 18:09.050
Apply an ice compress.

18:17.780 --> 18:19.360
At least you had the sense

18:19.470 --> 18:21.060
to call in a colleague with
the Engineering Department crew

18:21.060 --> 18:21.950
to help you out.

18:23.400 --> 18:24.240
In the future,

18:24.470 --> 18:26.200
if you encounter
this kind of situation again,

18:26.200 --> 18:28.000
you can also come to me directly.

18:30.370 --> 18:31.100
Are you okay?

18:41.620 --> 18:44.010
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

18:47.830 --> 18:48.590
Miyu.

18:48.880 --> 18:49.350
Miyu.

18:49.430 --> 18:50.270
Come here.

18:50.320 --> 18:51.120
Sit.

18:51.350 --> 18:52.370
I want to ask you a question.

18:52.370 --> 18:53.420
Sit.

18:54.280 --> 18:55.010
I'm asking you,

18:55.010 --> 18:56.960
how did you get so close to Black Card Ji?

18:56.960 --> 18:58.550
Yeah, teach us

18:58.550 --> 19:00.580
your tricks too.

19:00.750 --> 19:01.870
Miyu,

19:02.000 --> 19:05.160
is that guy the type who is cold
on the outside but warm on the inside?

19:05.160 --> 19:08.030
Cold as ice on the surface,

19:08.050 --> 19:09.510
but once he commits to you,

19:09.550 --> 19:11.810
he will go through fire and water for you.

19:13.630 --> 19:15.330
You read too many wish-fulfillment novels.

19:15.330 --> 19:16.860
What's wrong with wish-fulfillment novels?

19:16.860 --> 19:18.930
A strong, beautiful,
and tragic female lead

19:18.930 --> 19:21.040
protected by a domineering CEO,

19:21.060 --> 19:24.560
outsmarting a bunch
of crazy and obsessive monsters.

19:24.630 --> 19:27.360
Dare you say your dopamine didn't spike?

19:27.380 --> 19:28.900
Didn't it spike?

19:29.700 --> 19:31.200
What are you all talking about?

19:31.200 --> 19:32.470
I don't understand at all.

19:32.470 --> 19:34.510
This is not the script of my life.

19:34.540 --> 19:36.510
It's okay, Miyu.

19:36.790 --> 19:38.830
We're already shipping it.

19:39.200 --> 19:41.720
With a mysterious VIP
giving you a boost, your life

19:41.720 --> 19:43.290
is about to take off.

19:45.960 --> 19:48.390
Shipped it.

19:48.720 --> 19:49.920
So sweet.

19:53.120 --> 19:53.880
Hello, Neil.

19:54.230 --> 19:55.070
Any updates?

19:55.620 --> 19:56.950
Happy birthday, Mr. Ji.

19:57.310 --> 19:58.000
Thank you.

19:58.350 --> 19:59.030
Mr. Ji,

19:59.030 --> 20:01.020
did you sign the contract with Landi?

20:01.020 --> 20:01.880
Yeah, it was me.

20:01.950 --> 20:03.720
I've signed it for a couple of weeks.

20:03.720 --> 20:04.650
Anything wrong?

20:09.660 --> 20:11.330
Andy is on this contract.

20:11.670 --> 20:14.890
And it seems that Landi is suing us

20:15.110 --> 20:18.410
for some loopholes in
the imported horses protection clause.

20:18.410 --> 20:19.450
Happy birthday.

20:19.720 --> 20:20.530
Okay, thank you.

20:20.530 --> 20:21.020
Please.

20:21.540 --> 20:22.870
Tell me more about that.

20:22.880 --> 20:23.740
Take your time.

20:25.680 --> 20:27.810
Tell Andy to get in touch with me.

20:28.110 --> 20:29.150
I'll wait for him.

20:30.480 --> 20:32.430
Happy birthday.

20:32.430 --> 20:33.650
Hello, Mr. Ji.

20:33.720 --> 20:34.900
Today is your birthday.

20:34.900 --> 20:36.980
On behalf of all the service staff
on the executive floor,

20:36.980 --> 20:38.510
I wish you a happy birthday.

20:39.480 --> 20:40.110
Thank you.

20:42.000 --> 20:42.740
Mr. Ji,

20:42.930 --> 20:43.750
our executive floor

20:43.750 --> 20:46.000
provides special
birthday services for guests.

20:46.000 --> 20:48.000
Private dining rooms for up to 20 guests,

20:48.000 --> 20:50.120
as well as party spaces
for up to 80 guests,

20:48.220 --> 20:48.810
[Dear Mr. Ji, in the year ahead,]

20:48.830 --> 20:49.070
[may your life be as
beautiful as poetry, filled with joy,]

20:49.070 --> 20:49.310
[sunshine,]

20:49.340 --> 20:49.980
[and surprises. Happy Birthday.]

20:50.140 --> 20:52.270
do not require advance reservations.

20:53.160 --> 20:53.790
Got it.

20:54.270 --> 20:55.440
Tell the others

20:55.440 --> 20:57.640
not to say happy birthday to me anymore.

20:59.480 --> 21:00.110
Mr. Ji,

21:00.110 --> 21:01.480
what would you like to eat?

21:01.480 --> 21:03.160
The usual. Thanks.

21:03.240 --> 21:03.720
Okay.

21:06.030 --> 21:06.640
Okay.

21:07.340 --> 21:08.640
If you need anything,

21:08.750 --> 21:10.030
please feel free to contact me.

21:10.030 --> 21:10.640
Okay.

21:10.670 --> 21:11.470
Thanks.

21:11.650 --> 21:12.720
[Andy]

21:18.720 --> 21:19.750
Is this Andy?

21:21.230 --> 21:21.860
Great.

21:22.130 --> 21:24.230
I have something to discuss with you.

21:24.750 --> 21:25.830
The kitchen

21:25.830 --> 21:27.200
is already preparing
the birthday fruit platter.

21:27.200 --> 21:28.330
Should we cancel it?

21:30.110 --> 21:31.120
Why cancel?

21:31.300 --> 21:33.820
Free items still need
to be put on the tab.

21:34.280 --> 21:35.520
Then who is going to deliver it?

21:35.520 --> 21:36.450
I'll arrange it.

21:37.160 --> 21:38.120
You guys,

21:38.320 --> 21:40.250
just need to keep your mouths shut.

21:46.310 --> 21:47.150
Miyu.

21:47.440 --> 21:49.340
Make sure the service for room 1812

21:49.340 --> 21:50.500
is spot on today.

21:50.830 --> 21:51.620
Later,

21:51.830 --> 21:53.870
I'll send you the birthday schedule.

21:53.870 --> 21:55.900
Set the mood right.

22:00.090 --> 22:01.050
Room service.

22:02.960 --> 22:04.440
Hello, room service.

22:06.240 --> 22:06.830
Mr. Ji.

22:06.830 --> 22:07.360
Wish...

22:07.380 --> 22:08.970
Just give it a quick sweep.

22:10.370 --> 22:11.170
Andy.

22:12.450 --> 22:13.850
Happy birthday.

22:16.440 --> 22:20.490
Since this incident
occured in the isolated facility,

22:20.620 --> 22:22.470
that was not under our control.

22:24.590 --> 22:26.850
We shouldn't be held responsible for it.

22:31.200 --> 22:32.760
We bought the horses,

22:32.780 --> 22:35.330
but they don't officially
belong to us yet.

22:37.240 --> 22:40.470
The seller shall be
responsible for any risks.

22:40.940 --> 22:41.920
This was clearly

22:41.920 --> 22:43.160
stated in the contract.

22:43.160 --> 22:44.160
The seller didn't have third-party

22:44.160 --> 22:46.020
disease coverage for the horses.

22:46.580 --> 22:47.680
They then infected

22:47.680 --> 22:48.960
all 100 high-value horses

22:48.960 --> 22:50.590
in quarantine.

22:50.920 --> 22:52.750
We lost over 10 million dollars.

22:53.650 --> 22:55.920
Now they want to shift
the blame to our hotel.

22:55.920 --> 22:57.270
Find the contract immediately.

22:57.270 --> 22:59.530
They can't dodge their responsibility.

23:00.120 --> 23:02.050
I'm looking for the contract here.

23:02.900 --> 23:03.630
But, Ji Feng,

23:04.200 --> 23:05.160
you signed the contract

23:05.160 --> 23:06.110
before you left.

23:07.170 --> 23:07.740
Hold on.

23:15.860 --> 23:17.510
The group just sent a formal notice.

23:17.510 --> 23:19.400
If this contract

23:19.400 --> 23:21.330
causes major final losses to the hotel,

23:21.330 --> 23:22.960
the manager who signed the contract

23:22.960 --> 23:24.890
will be blacklisted internationally.

23:24.890 --> 23:25.950
Do you understand?

23:26.200 --> 23:28.590
This means that in
European and American hotel systems,

23:28.590 --> 23:32.240
you will never be hired.

23:41.330 --> 23:42.110
Ji Feng.

23:42.250 --> 23:42.790
Excuse me.

23:42.790 --> 23:43.700
You can't come in.

23:43.700 --> 23:44.440
Who are you?

23:44.440 --> 23:45.290
Mind your own business.

23:45.290 --> 23:45.990
Ji Feng.

23:47.340 --> 23:48.620
You can't come in.

23:49.000 --> 23:50.200
Do you know who I am?

23:53.240 --> 23:55.880
Happy birthday.

23:57.880 --> 23:58.420
Mr. Duan,

23:58.450 --> 23:59.180
we...

24:02.790 --> 24:04.030
Ta-da!

24:04.030 --> 24:04.720
-Happy birthday!
-What is this?

24:04.720 --> 24:05.850
Happy birthday!

24:05.870 --> 24:06.750
Happy birthday!

24:06.750 --> 24:07.350
Thank you.

24:07.550 --> 24:08.270
-Happy birthday.
-Thank you.

24:08.270 --> 24:09.200
Happy birthday!

24:09.200 --> 24:10.300
-Just a little noise.
-Happy birthday!

24:10.300 --> 24:12.480
-To help you shake the dust off the ceiling.
-Happy birthday!

24:12.480 --> 24:13.440
Are you trying to shake the ceiling

24:13.440 --> 24:14.900
or blow my head off?

24:18.000 --> 24:18.730
Wait a minute.

24:18.730 --> 24:20.080
Help me entertain the guests.

24:20.080 --> 24:21.030
Mr. Duan, excuse me.

24:21.030 --> 24:21.750
I need to take a call.

24:21.750 --> 24:22.550
Excuse me for a moment.

24:22.550 --> 24:23.250
Go.

24:26.010 --> 24:28.200
Let's go party!

24:30.480 --> 24:31.030
Come on.

24:31.030 --> 24:31.640
Attendant.

24:31.640 --> 24:33.240
Come here and build a champagne tower.

24:33.240 --> 24:35.100
If you break it, you have to drink.

24:35.490 --> 24:36.720
Close the curtains.

24:36.720 --> 24:37.240
It's broad daylight.

24:37.240 --> 24:38.270
There's no atmosphere for drinking.

24:38.270 --> 24:39.400
I'll close the curtains.

24:39.400 --> 24:40.530
Queue up some songs.

24:41.640 --> 24:42.440
Queue up the songs.

24:42.140 --> 24:51.880
[Meeting Details]

24:42.460 --> 24:43.200
Hi, Andy.

24:44.170 --> 24:45.670
I can't find the contract.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.300
Are these okay?

24:48.750 --> 24:51.210
Go find the backup copy
of your contract now.

24:51.480 --> 24:51.960
Hurry.

24:52.680 --> 24:54.410
I can't find the backup either.

24:54.590 --> 24:58.530
[Meeting Details]

24:54.630 --> 24:55.240
I suspect

24:55.240 --> 24:56.640
Landi bribed someone in our hotel

24:56.640 --> 24:58.680
to destroy the contract and its backup.

24:58.680 --> 25:00.340
They're clearly out to get us.

25:02.240 --> 25:03.240
Speaking of that,

25:03.240 --> 25:05.430
I signed a memorandum with them.

25:05.830 --> 25:08.200
All the necessary information
and signatures are there.

25:08.140 --> 25:15.100
[Meeting Details]

25:08.750 --> 25:09.680
I'll look for it right now.

25:09.680 --> 25:11.350
You don't still have it, do you?

25:11.350 --> 25:13.000
It's just my way of doing things.

25:13.000 --> 25:15.330
I have to.
There are so many traps to avoid.

25:28.000 --> 25:30.070
[Horse Purchase and Sales Contract]

25:44.030 --> 25:46.830
Happy birthday to you.

25:46.940 --> 25:49.930
Happy birthday to you.

25:50.010 --> 25:53.350
Happy birthday to you.

25:53.350 --> 25:56.960
Happy birthday to you.

25:57.090 --> 25:58.400
Happy birthday.

26:04.840 --> 26:05.350
Are you okay?

26:05.350 --> 26:06.750
Who pushed me?

26:06.750 --> 26:08.210
My buddy's cake is ruined.

26:26.630 --> 26:28.290
Is this thing important?

26:28.750 --> 26:29.320
Get out.

26:30.930 --> 26:31.740
Get out!

26:32.850 --> 26:33.950
Let's go.

26:37.560 --> 26:38.190
Mr. Ji.

26:38.220 --> 26:39.320
I told you to get out!

26:39.320 --> 26:42.980
Do you people on the executive floor
not understand human speech?

27:04.320 --> 27:06.030
I said I wasn't celebrating my birthday.

27:06.030 --> 27:08.110
Yet you brought a bunch of people
into my room to make a mess.

27:08.110 --> 27:09.730
I didn't bring these people in.

27:09.730 --> 27:11.130
Then who brought them in?

27:11.130 --> 27:12.230
Did they break down the door?

27:12.230 --> 27:13.630
You opened the door

27:13.650 --> 27:14.740
and let them in.

27:15.110 --> 27:16.960
And you even made
some flower arrangement for me.

27:16.960 --> 27:18.400
Did you think by showing off like that

27:18.400 --> 27:20.060
I would give you a good review?

27:20.480 --> 27:21.110
It's not like that.

27:21.110 --> 27:22.000
Let me ask you,

27:22.220 --> 27:24.480
how does your
HSKP Department serve guests?

27:24.480 --> 27:25.440
Is it based on the guests' needs,

27:25.440 --> 27:26.840
or your own preferences?

27:27.130 --> 27:28.140
What a mess.

27:28.350 --> 27:30.550
Do you believe I'll complain about you?

27:30.820 --> 27:32.460
I already told you,

27:32.650 --> 27:34.150
I didn't bring the guests in,

27:34.150 --> 27:36.090
and this mess wasn't
caused by our executive floor.

27:36.090 --> 27:37.380
On what grounds are you
complaining about me?

27:37.380 --> 27:39.300
My birthday is my privacy.

27:39.380 --> 27:40.160
Whether I celebrate it

27:40.160 --> 27:41.710
and who I invite to celebrate with me,

27:41.710 --> 27:42.800
is for me to decide.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.680
You're violating my privacy right now.

27:44.680 --> 27:45.440
That alone

27:45.470 --> 27:46.550
is enough for me to file
a complaint against you.

27:46.550 --> 27:48.360
You say I invaded your privacy, right?

27:48.360 --> 27:49.660
Then as a consumer,

27:49.740 --> 27:51.440
you didn't respect
my right to know either.

27:51.440 --> 27:52.830
How did I not respect your right to know?

27:52.830 --> 27:53.680
Mr. Ji,

27:54.030 --> 27:55.290
do I need to remind you?

27:55.360 --> 27:56.740
Just a month ago,

27:56.920 --> 27:58.270
in the hotel where you
were the general manager,

27:58.270 --> 27:59.680
you kept telling me

27:59.680 --> 28:00.880
that the underwear on my bed

28:00.880 --> 28:02.550
was left by the previous guest.

28:02.550 --> 28:03.830
You said, "Mrs. Nie,

28:03.830 --> 28:05.160
please rest assured.

28:05.160 --> 28:06.440
I have looked into it.

28:06.440 --> 28:07.400
This underwear

28:07.400 --> 28:09.100
has absolutely nothing
to do with your husband."

28:09.100 --> 28:10.500
Nie Yucheng is innocent.

28:11.030 --> 28:12.500
I didn't say your husband was innocent.

28:12.500 --> 28:13.070
Right.

28:13.230 --> 28:14.910
You didn't use the word "innocent."

28:14.910 --> 28:16.680
But you spun the lie so perfectly

28:16.680 --> 28:18.550
that you made me believe he was innocent.

28:18.550 --> 28:19.640
You made me believe

28:19.640 --> 28:21.200
my marriage was rock solid.

28:21.200 --> 28:22.350
I didn't lie.

28:22.700 --> 28:23.160
I...

28:23.550 --> 28:24.270
I just...

28:26.490 --> 28:28.090
I just didn't tell the whole truth.

28:28.090 --> 28:29.710
Not telling the whole truth?

28:29.790 --> 28:31.070
You were taking things out of context,

28:31.070 --> 28:31.880
confusing right and wrong,

28:31.880 --> 28:32.640
misleading me with selective details,

28:32.640 --> 28:34.840
and making sweeping generalizations.

28:35.250 --> 28:37.480
Did your conscience
allow you to say that?

28:37.480 --> 28:39.110
Is that how you treat your
guests and the trust

28:39.110 --> 28:41.310
they place in you—with such hypocrisy?

28:41.320 --> 28:42.880
You keep saying

28:43.380 --> 28:44.480
you serve your guests

28:44.480 --> 28:45.540
and think for them.

28:46.110 --> 28:48.440
You speak in such high-sounding words,

28:48.560 --> 28:50.480
but what you do is so hypocritical

28:50.500 --> 28:51.710
and perfunctory.

28:52.100 --> 28:53.140
Mr. Ji,

28:53.160 --> 28:54.840
are you really thinking for your guests?

28:54.840 --> 28:57.000
I think you're probably
just using sweet words

28:57.000 --> 28:59.400
to build a persona
as a gold-medal manager.

28:59.920 --> 29:01.270
Your own marriage...

29:01.390 --> 29:02.550
Your own marriage failed,

29:02.550 --> 29:03.550
and you don't examine yourself,

29:03.550 --> 29:04.750
but blame me instead.

29:04.860 --> 29:06.200
Don't you think you're ridiculous?

29:06.200 --> 29:07.780
Yes, I am ridiculous.

29:07.800 --> 29:09.460
I'm the laughingstock
of the whole world now.

29:09.460 --> 29:10.200
But don't you think

29:10.200 --> 29:11.720
you have a part in this?

29:11.800 --> 29:12.750
If it weren't for you

29:12.750 --> 29:14.310
helping my ex-husband lie to me,

29:14.310 --> 29:15.240
would my life now

29:15.240 --> 29:16.820
be reduced to this?

29:17.270 --> 29:18.750
You say you think for your guests.

29:18.750 --> 29:19.920
You say all you think about

29:19.920 --> 29:20.830
are the guests' interests.

29:20.830 --> 29:21.550
I think all you think about

29:21.550 --> 29:22.790
are your own interests.

29:22.790 --> 29:23.960
Your KPI.

29:23.960 --> 29:24.240
I...

29:24.260 --> 29:25.240
If Nie Yucheng couldn't

29:25.240 --> 29:26.350
bring you a few clients,

29:26.350 --> 29:28.630
would you need to suck
up to him so desperately?

29:28.630 --> 29:29.690
The funny thing is,

29:29.720 --> 29:31.440
I even thought after
I came to Purong Hotel

29:31.440 --> 29:32.590
you had been helping me.

29:32.590 --> 29:34.440
Actually, it's because of
your guilty conscience, right?

29:34.440 --> 29:36.400
Because you are
my ex-husband's accomplice.

29:36.400 --> 29:37.960
No matter how many masks you wear,

29:37.960 --> 29:39.880
you're a hypocritical wretch to the bone!

29:39.880 --> 29:40.710
If I were you,

29:40.730 --> 29:43.130
I'd look in the mirror
and examine myself carefully.

29:43.130 --> 29:44.740
If it weren't for your own
weakness and incompetence,

29:44.740 --> 29:46.270
coveting wealth and glory,

29:46.270 --> 29:47.850
blindly pleasing your ex-husband,

29:47.850 --> 29:49.810
how could he be so fearless

29:49.840 --> 29:51.850
and act wildly right under your nose?

29:51.850 --> 29:53.130
You're looking for an accomplice, right?

29:53.130 --> 29:54.460
Let me tell you, Xu Miyu,

29:54.640 --> 29:57.240
your ex-husband's
biggest accomplice is you!

30:01.930 --> 30:04.870
I want to file a complaint against
an attendant from the HSKP Department.

30:04.870 --> 30:05.700
Executive floor,

30:05.700 --> 30:06.550
Xu Miyu.

30:07.000 --> 30:08.170
She was rude to a guest

30:08.170 --> 30:10.230
and had a terrible service attitude.

30:55.850 --> 30:56.850
[Album]

30:56.890 --> 30:57.460
[Photo]

30:57.740 --> 31:01.120
[Horse Purchase and Sales Contract]

31:07.130 --> 31:09.140
[Horse Ownership]

31:12.780 --> 31:14.530
[Send]

31:14.740 --> 31:15.590
[Inbox]

31:35.730 --> 31:36.490
Hi, Andy.

31:36.700 --> 31:37.760
That's great.

31:38.270 --> 31:39.470
We're gonna win it.

31:40.330 --> 31:41.860
I can't believe we made it.

31:41.970 --> 31:43.300
Man, you are a true hero.

31:44.440 --> 31:45.520
How I wish I were.

31:46.170 --> 31:48.200
I only ask to be treated like a person.

31:48.200 --> 31:49.130
What did you say?

31:50.560 --> 31:51.920
What I just said is...

31:54.100 --> 31:54.850
Forget it.

31:55.130 --> 31:56.790
I don't know how to express it.

31:57.320 --> 31:57.960
Ji Feng.

31:58.280 --> 31:59.000
Listen.

31:59.810 --> 32:01.870
You should have a drink to celebrate.

32:02.670 --> 32:03.470
Good idea.

32:03.580 --> 32:04.530
Have a good night.

32:04.530 --> 32:05.860
Okay, have a good night.

32:34.210 --> 32:35.830
You say you think for your guests.

32:35.830 --> 32:36.960
You say all you think about

32:36.960 --> 32:37.880
is the guests' interests.

32:37.880 --> 32:38.550
I think all you think about

32:38.550 --> 32:39.830
are your own interests.

32:39.830 --> 32:41.030
Your KPI!

32:41.400 --> 32:42.200
Isn't it just that Nie Yucheng

32:42.200 --> 32:44.240
can bring you some client resources?

32:44.240 --> 32:46.530
Do you have to try
so hard to suck up to him?

32:46.640 --> 32:47.540
I tell you.

32:47.590 --> 32:49.550
You are an accomplice of my ex-husband.

32:49.550 --> 32:51.110
No matter how many masks you wear,

32:51.110 --> 32:53.440
you're a hypocritical wretch to the bone!

33:04.710 --> 33:07.110
[Employee Schedule]

33:07.110 --> 33:14.850
[Xu Miyu, 18F,
Morning Shift, Bad Review]

33:24.960 --> 33:25.410
Miyu.

33:25.470 --> 33:28.200
You haven't taken out
the seasoning packets yet.

33:37.410 --> 33:38.210
We got paid.

33:39.260 --> 33:41.050
Full bonus, 5,500.

33:41.200 --> 33:42.730
How much did you get, Xiang?

33:43.440 --> 33:44.110
Eight thousand?

33:43.930 --> 33:44.590
[Minfu Bank]

33:44.960 --> 33:45.590
Nine thousand?

33:45.150 --> 33:46.950
[Transaction Notification:
Transaction Amount 7,350 RMB]

33:46.160 --> 33:46.960
Ten thousand?

33:47.000 --> 33:48.130
How much did you get?

33:48.440 --> 33:49.400
Not that much.

33:49.920 --> 33:51.450
You have to treat me anyway.

33:53.360 --> 33:55.820
[Transaction Notification:
Transaction Amount 2,800 RMB]

34:24.110 --> 34:25.310
Hello, Officer Wang.

34:25.760 --> 34:26.620
Ms. Xu,

34:26.880 --> 34:27.770
I'm calling to inform you

34:27.770 --> 34:29.550
that the suspect
in the rental fraud and theft case

34:29.550 --> 34:30.480
has been caught.

34:30.739 --> 34:31.340
Really?

34:32.550 --> 34:34.080
But you should be prepared.

34:34.150 --> 34:36.750
Your financial loss
is likely unrecoverable.

34:38.190 --> 34:39.070
I understand.

35:11.230 --> 35:16.630
[Road closed]

35:15.070 --> 35:16.030
Xu Miyu.

35:19.920 --> 35:22.030
Are you Ms. Xu Miyu?

35:22.670 --> 35:24.270
Who are you?

35:24.290 --> 35:25.690
You don't know who we are?

35:26.070 --> 35:27.670
Then what are you hiding for?

35:28.710 --> 35:30.440
Not answering calls

35:30.460 --> 35:31.580
or messages.

35:32.190 --> 35:32.840
What?

35:33.000 --> 35:34.000
Trying to renege?

35:36.650 --> 35:39.380
No, my bonus got deducted recently.

35:39.510 --> 35:41.330
I really don't have money.

35:41.380 --> 35:43.300
Can you give me 2 more days?

35:43.420 --> 35:45.050
I sympathize with you, Ms. Xu,

35:45.050 --> 35:46.320
but telling me this

35:46.340 --> 35:47.440
is useless.

35:47.440 --> 35:48.800
Everyone who can't pay back

35:48.800 --> 35:49.930
says the same thing.

35:50.040 --> 35:51.980
Can you say something new?

35:52.810 --> 35:55.830
Even if you make up a story,
make it a good one.

35:56.890 --> 35:58.340
Don't be nervous, Ms. Xu.

35:58.650 --> 36:00.520
We are just workers too.

36:01.840 --> 36:03.690
I hope you can understand.

36:03.720 --> 36:04.990
Just easily

36:05.070 --> 36:06.250
give us the money,

36:06.320 --> 36:07.880
so we can all go home and rest early.

36:07.880 --> 36:08.780
Right?

36:08.800 --> 36:09.400
I...

36:10.290 --> 36:12.760
I really don't have a single cent.

36:12.780 --> 36:14.070
Give me 2 more days.

36:14.070 --> 36:16.000
I will definitely find a way, okay?

36:17.400 --> 36:18.280
What should we do?

36:18.280 --> 36:19.410
She said 2 more days.

36:21.670 --> 36:22.400
How about this?

36:22.400 --> 36:24.530
I'll treat you to some coffee,

36:24.550 --> 36:25.990
and we can talk somewhere else.

36:25.990 --> 36:28.550
Ms. Xu, you have more to say to us?

36:29.360 --> 36:30.210
Not really.

36:35.670 --> 36:36.590
How about this?

36:36.640 --> 36:38.010
We know a place

36:38.280 --> 36:39.870
where it's easy

36:40.080 --> 36:41.550
to make money overnight.

36:42.280 --> 36:43.010
How about it?

36:43.570 --> 36:45.260
I know you're not the type

36:45.290 --> 36:47.070
to intentionally default on a debt.

36:47.070 --> 36:47.600
Let's go.

36:48.220 --> 36:49.480
Let's go drink coffee.

36:49.480 --> 36:50.360
Let me go.

36:50.640 --> 36:51.840
You're quite strong.

36:52.440 --> 36:53.320
Let me go!

36:53.320 --> 36:54.280
These are my colleagues.

36:54.280 --> 36:55.030
I'll scream!

36:55.050 --> 36:55.960
Okay.

36:56.060 --> 36:58.350
- Call your colleagues over then.
- Let me go!

36:58.350 --> 36:59.070
Let her go!

37:01.070 --> 37:02.360
I heard everything.

37:02.750 --> 37:04.080
I'll give you the money.

37:06.260 --> 37:07.000
If you said that earlier,

37:07.000 --> 37:08.520
this wouldn't have happened.

37:08.520 --> 37:09.030
Come on.

37:09.250 --> 37:10.530
[Lu Ming; Ming]

37:10.560 --> 37:10.800
[Loading]

37:10.950 --> 37:12.330
[Payment to an individual]

37:16.110 --> 37:16.880
Excuse me,

37:16.880 --> 37:18.700
are you her colleague, sir?

37:18.730 --> 37:19.860
Leave immediately,

37:19.890 --> 37:21.220
or I'll call the police.

37:22.550 --> 37:23.150
Thank you.

37:23.400 --> 37:23.930
Let's go.

37:30.810 --> 37:31.660
Are you okay?

37:33.070 --> 37:33.730
I'm fine.

37:36.430 --> 37:37.090
Thank you.

37:37.850 --> 37:38.650
It's nothing.

37:40.390 --> 37:42.520
I will pay you back as soon as possible.

38:01.680 --> 38:02.590
[Your business loan
has been automatically repaid]

38:02.610 --> 38:03.710
[for ¥5,000. Your payment
for this month has been settled]

38:08.440 --> 38:10.480
Life is truly ironic.

38:10.710 --> 38:11.800
The ones you love

38:11.820 --> 38:13.230
and trust

38:13.440 --> 38:16.330
betray and leave you one by one.

38:17.570 --> 38:19.910
The one who repeatedly
saves you from trouble

38:19.910 --> 38:20.710
is always the one

38:20.710 --> 38:22.840
you should cross paths with the least.

38:23.840 --> 38:26.840
I'm starting to hate my own
pitifulness and weakness.

38:34.550 --> 38:35.400
Room service.

38:41.320 --> 38:42.800
Hello, room service.

39:17.000 --> 39:17.810
Mr. Ji,

39:17.840 --> 39:18.720
you're here.

39:46.800 --> 39:47.670
Can you sew?

39:49.430 --> 39:51.030
Otherwise, sew it yourself.

40:11.060 --> 40:11.550
Done.

40:11.810 --> 40:12.410
Thank you.

40:20.300 --> 40:21.000
By the way.

40:22.190 --> 40:23.360
About last night,

40:23.710 --> 40:24.400
thank you.

40:25.620 --> 40:28.390
[IOU]

40:27.550 --> 40:28.280
This is the IOU.

40:28.280 --> 40:28.760
No need.

40:29.400 --> 40:30.400
It was no trouble.

40:31.920 --> 40:32.980
You must accept it.

40:33.070 --> 40:34.330
I don't want to owe you.

40:55.070 --> 40:55.800
Miyu.

40:56.880 --> 40:57.360
Sit.

41:07.370 --> 41:08.050
Miyu.

41:09.190 --> 41:10.670
Did you

41:12.190 --> 41:13.360
offend Madam Cailu?

41:15.110 --> 41:15.840
No.

41:16.510 --> 41:17.360
Why do you ask?

41:19.480 --> 41:20.670
A couple of days ago,

41:21.280 --> 41:21.920
I heard her

41:21.920 --> 41:23.860
talking to someone on the phone.

41:24.670 --> 41:25.360
She said

41:25.840 --> 41:27.040
she wants to fire you.

41:29.070 --> 41:29.840
What?

41:31.320 --> 41:31.960
Why?

41:32.590 --> 41:33.590
I don't know,

41:33.920 --> 41:35.320
b-but I heard it with my own ears.

41:35.320 --> 41:36.450
I'm not lying to you.

41:37.710 --> 41:38.970
That's impossible.

41:39.550 --> 41:40.950
I've never offended her.

41:43.070 --> 41:44.730
When did you hear her say that?

41:46.280 --> 41:47.630
Last...

41:47.920 --> 41:48.920
Last Tuesday.

41:49.470 --> 41:50.560
In the Linen Room.

41:51.000 --> 41:53.000
I was outside and heard her talking.

41:53.480 --> 41:55.650
She was speaking very anxiously.

41:55.880 --> 41:58.080
It seemed like something had happened.

42:14.440 --> 42:16.030
Last time you asked me
to get 2 bottles of shampoo

42:16.030 --> 42:17.430
from 2 different places,

42:17.480 --> 42:18.610
what was that about?

42:20.550 --> 42:23.070
I can't tell you
too many details right now.

42:23.590 --> 42:25.150
The whole story hasn't

42:25.440 --> 42:27.100
been fully investigated yet.

42:28.690 --> 42:29.840
Then give me a sample.

42:29.840 --> 42:30.670
I'll help you look into it.
